Package: FARS
Type: Package
Title: Facilitates Analysis of FARS Data
Version: 1.0.0
Date: 2018-03-22
Depends: R (>= 3.0.0)
Author: Sam Thomas <samuel.thomas12@gmail.com>
Maintainer: Sam Thomas <samuel.thomas12@gmail.com>
Description: The FARS package contains a set of useful functions to facilitate
    analysis of data from the U.S. Department of Transportaion Fatality Analysis Reporting
    System. The package allows users to easily load data, filter data by year, 
    and count and map fataility events by year, month, and U.S. state.
License: GPL (>= 2)
Encoding: UTF-8
